{"tid":1026392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國瑜深夜直播：「全台灣都欠高雄人！」","createTime":"2019-02-18T05:40:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T15:07:40.000Z","uid":41404,"like":3,"dislike":127,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"10015b41fc9ff33c277fcfb94f54f73506981f39","tid":1026392,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T05:40:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2701836\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2701836&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgPRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=dd2565de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2701836&h=d335265b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2701836</a><br />\n<br />\n中國高雄市長韓國瑜昨晚開臉書直播，痛陳全台灣人都欠高雄，高雄為台灣扛重工業卻汙染環境，中央應該回饋；臉書粉專只是堵藍反駁，不是全台灣欠高雄，是全國民黨都欠高雄一個交代。<br />\n韓國瑜昨晚透過臉書直播再論述兩岸政策，他質疑蔡英文總統不愛中華民國、不要九二共識、也不敢台灣獨立，我們（台灣）該到哪裡去？因為要推銷高雄產品、要吸引觀光客，所以他必須講出九二共識，爭取和平做生意，但不用天天講，只要大家知道他的想法就行了。<br />\n韓國瑜進一步抱怨，行政院長蘇貞昌上台後，要求高市府申請前瞻計畫補助要全部改寫，這是什麼意思？行政院本就應該協助高雄，他表示全台灣都欠高雄人，因為高雄犧牲環境，發展台灣重工業，污染這麼嚴重，高雄以一個城市力量，支撐台灣重工業發展，當然應該回饋高雄，結果補助款卻要高市重寫計畫，甚麼意思、希望高雄失敗嗎、繼續窮困嗎、還是希望韓國瑜施政上摔死？"},{"pid":"925f47f913db3ad4db402e9534c7e2f6fb4f9bcb","tid":1026392,"uid":193893,"like":180,"dislike":1,"score":179,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T05:46:42.000Z","msg":"今期流行 流行高雄陳雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全台灣都久高雄一個交代！皇天擊殺全台灣！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"633d73eff12937b1e6382d5b1a808cb51a816478","tid":1026392,"uid":17641,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T05:46:43.000Z","msg":"韓爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f294786f6e83752dae8351e02f1d3442c7de682f","tid":1026392,"uid":191926,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T05:48:11.000Z","msg":"韓總<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b978f024db8166b6d6d35c14115e4cba0ffcd27","tid":1026392,"uid":71657,"like":157,"dislike":8,"score":149,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T05:48:25.000Z","msg":"唔知點解會錯覺睇成韓國周子瑜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69d9779b129cbe7b5e7b26dc9008ee2d37c9695e","tid":1026392,"uid":35790,"like":63,"dislike":1,"score":62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T05:49:53.000Z","msg":"越來越覺得支那瑜似&quot;國師&quot;<br />\n成日唔記得食藥"},{"pid":"dc2eb20746100c6397d1ea01e1bbda7cddcdfe98","tid":1026392,"uid":53811,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T05:53:09.000Z","msg":"估唔到佢走國屍路線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ddcd33e895551938b99271e5aae870254cf41ad","tid":1026392,"uid":33890,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T05:53:34.000Z","msg":"佢話全台灣欠高雄人當然吹大左，<br />\n但民進黨執政高雄20年話國民黨欠高雄一個交代<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be11f1fd8238aa72bc2b8dff3968f6d5643f9855","tid":1026392,"uid":190333,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"2ddcd33e895551938b99271e5aae870254cf41ad","tid":1026392,"uid":33890,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T05:53:34.000Z","msg":"佢話全台灣欠高雄人當然吹大左，<br />\n但民進黨執政高雄20年話國民黨欠高雄一個交代<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T05:58:42.000Z","msg":"可能講緊再之前白賊義既年代<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0153e658c092a160b88a49f926585ff6759c1497","tid":1026392,"uid":48631,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T05:59:45.000Z","msg":"慘得過高雄牛屎佬buy條痴線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c88beb3d0d19a210e0414378230197e692dcac05","tid":1026392,"uid":18012,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T06:00:45